{"tid":214160,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搬出黎住","createTime":"2017-04-23T15:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T16:31:41.000Z","uid":12532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fd2832e32aa69bef34a31091f145b5fabf460718","tid":214160,"uid":12532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"而家租金咁貴 身邊朋友個個都話好唔抵 儲首期買樓好過<br />\n但係我已經冇私人空間左廿幾年 (三個人一間房) 真係好想試下自己住同埋養隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢度有冇廿幾歲巴絲已經搬左出黎住? 分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPs 其實我仲想搵人合租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bab1a4cbcf0c57e63fd968e1ebf9732260fd35c","tid":214160,"uid":21027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:23:36.000Z","msg":"Lm 搵合租"},{"pid":"1cc86edab978c2f2f0dbe1b230209ca48f40a519","tid":214160,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:24:45.000Z","msg":"同朋友夾緊租 我有隻狗<br />\n每人5000 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然每個月要慳慳地地使<br />\n但自由係無價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係個人開心d <br />\n<br />\n利申： 最憎屋企人依依哦哦"},{"pid":"d2180801dceeed5e0dcb4f022faf9a65a43551c9","tid":214160,"uid":12532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:27:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同朋友夾緊租 我有隻狗<br />\n每人5000 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然每個月要慳慳地地使<br />\n但自由係無價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係個人開心d <br />\n<br />\n利申： 最憎屋企人依依哦哦</blockquote><br />\n介唔介意講下 你租邊區 同埋係屬於咩類型既樓? (eg 屋苑/唐/村屋)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都好想養狗狗 一貓一狗係我目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但貓好似比較易養 所以想養左貓先"},{"pid":"d9685b74fa5710f95bf93c25feb98c7bcaf69953","tid":214160,"uid":12532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:28:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Lm 搵合租</blockquote><br />\n巴打有興趣租邊區?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2f070f4f00addb9f8400168cbc0e1f5fb9df8c","tid":214160,"uid":65333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:29:28.000Z","msg":"裝修緊, 準備開始自己一個住, 怕有d唔習慣, 會好靜"},{"pid":"eb699e4d63192fdfb95b054d311c2994c6641d29","tid":214160,"uid":12532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:32:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>裝修緊, 準備開始自己一個住, 怕有d唔習慣, 會好靜</blockquote><br />\n一個人租好貴喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得閒邀請多啲朋友上去玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1cce7271aa48c5a13d46b208e60dd95101149a","tid":214160,"uid":19769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:41:42.000Z","msg":"LM 夾租<br />\n25歲巴求夾"},{"pid":"a3b1bda7ed97f7bd0a741fd0205e2d629cc2fe7c","tid":214160,"uid":19769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Lm 搵合租</blockquote><br />\n巴打有興趣租邊區?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅磡點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a41ce615a89b9a4b177d4258dac08c92dd1e723","tid":214160,"uid":12532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Lm 搵合租</blockquote><br />\n巴打有興趣租邊區?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅磡點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅磡交通方便 多食肆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你budget 幾多?"},{"pid":"4bd896043011691481d74012125b3a21ac10bf97","tid":214160,"uid":12532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:51:29.000Z",